rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I hear there's an amazing
sculptor in Invidia!

rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently, he's such a master that no one
can match him when it comes to sculpting
the current Invidian Queen, Queen Raguel.

rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I'd love for someone like
that to create a sculpture
using Gulan wood, just once!

rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I wonder if that will ever
happen, if our trade with
Invidia progresses.

rows.label: tlk41400021_03_msg0005
rows.name:
How about calling the piece "The
Wooden Queen"? What do you think!
